1. We prepared the files "testConnect.py" and "zhihantest.py," these files are used by Akira and Zhihan to verify whether they can access the database via code.
   For Akira  DB, "testConnect.py" 
   For Zhihan DB, "zhihantest.py"

2. We prepared the files "akiraDB.py" and "zhihanDB.py," these files are used by Akira and Zhihan to verify the contents of the data.
   For Akira  DB, "akiraDB.py" 
   For Zhihan DB, "zhihanDB.py"

3. requirements: psycopg2_binary, python-dotenv